cs.SE, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.PL. 

This paper is about improving code completion in Python, which is a software engineering task. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses natural language processing techniques to mine API usages, which suggests a connection to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses a nearest neighbor classifier, which is a machine learning technique, suggesting a connection to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques to identify the best matching usage, suggesting a connection to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper is about programming languages and APIs, suggesting a connection to cs.PL (Programming Languages).
